        "subject": "LU-19874 osd-wbcfs: rename statics to avoid conflicts",
        "message": "LU-19874 osd-wbcfs: rename statics to avoid conflicts\n\nThe OSDs in Lustre often use similar names for static\nvariables. Add 'wbcfs' to a number of static variables\nin osd-wbcfs to avoid conflicts when compiling the OSD\ninto the kernel image.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I7ca69532d844235cfcd63c31c3c3f9cc6507a6df\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63986\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\n"
